{"tid":1659793,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"A0 唔甘心A0 grad","createTime":"2019-10-17T06:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T08:57:45.000Z","uid":333653,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43f3912059becacd20406f80f7fc2d315f0201f4","tid":1659793,"uid":333653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:53:20.000Z","msg":"小弟自從入u玩咗唔少Ocamp <br />\n上過下頹莊<br />\n住過下hall咁<br />\n努力入多項運動u team <br />\n個人信心多咗唔少<br />\n已經由以前內向頹毒<br />\n到宜家係咁宜都算執好咗個look<br />\n見到女仔都會自帶話題<br />\n有啲女仔都話我個look好<br />\n<br />\n但A0嘅我習慣咗一個人<br />\n而且以前好多女仔<br />\n因為我嘅頹look 內向 自卑<br />\n而狠狠拒絕咗我<br />\n所以我宜家都仲有啲心理陰影<br />\n<br />\n但係近日識咗個女仔朋友<br />\n佢都好似習慣咗一個人<br />\n而且仲好enjoy一個人<br />\n我自問同佢玩得黎幾開心<br />\n平時ig都會對對方嘅story留言同傾計<br />\n間唔中會WhatsApp下<br />\n而且我地係u 都會經常撞到面<br />\n間唔中成班fd gathering佢都必定出現<br />\n<br />\n有時見到佢發嬲個樣都覺得幾得意<br />\n但係我係唔係應該去馬溝佢<br />\n我份人比較喜歡自由<br />\n或者都諗到佢都鐘意一個人無軀無束<br />\n定係A0 grad算數<br />\n讀埋今年就 grad"},{"pid":"5edfd3e9a6dbb94d46fccc938907adbb46ce4ff0","tid":1659793,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4d499329d472259180091d5d088653166ee9310a","tid":1659793,"uid":44035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"你個標題咪答左自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac256148aef17f34177f0f66ab8866fe3f302d24","tid":1659793,"uid":54472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d499329d472259180091d5d088653166ee9310a","tid":1659793,"uid":44035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:54:40.000Z","msg":"你個標題咪答左自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"咪就係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"